descriptionHTML:
Glorious Galaxy Watch Face for Android Wear Watch

One application contains 3 watch faces.

Supports any screen resolution and form.

Please make sure your watch is running Android Wear 5.0
Android Wear devices only, this is not a widget or live wallpaper

To install:
1. After install run 'Resync app' on Android Wear App.
2. Long press your android wear watch and choose this application as your watch face
3. You may have to wait a minute or so to transfer to your watch over Bluetooth

If you have any issues please contact me.

Please rate. Thanks!
comments: Ugh Very choppy on my Asus Zenwatch 2. Would give 5 stars if it had date, steps, weather, battery, options the other FREE watch faces have it. I paid for this one and have nothing but the time......
Meh Great idea. Lags on 360. I also paid for this, option to remove your logo please.
Great idea Animation is just too choppy
Awesome if not so lag Moto 360, not sure if it will kill my battery.
